{"tid":1568751,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有無諗過依家休班狗唔帶委任證就執法","createTime":"2019-09-14T11:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T17:00:53.000Z","uid":174953,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dc2a14f7ffe5697c90a7b375e7d5676de09587b3","tid":1568751,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"咁如果有人帶住伸縮警棍或手扣，就代表佢係休班克警？<br />\n<br />\n咁佢咪可以執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正都唔洗帶委任證執法<br />\n<br />\n咁之後如果有人咁做咪好危險，周街都係克警都可以隨時捉人，咁如果一個唔小心捉我依啲撐警藍絲我咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要比人仆幾棍，又要比人搭住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仇都無得報<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚驚添，我警告你地黃屍唔好亂黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e996a4431fe5e1aa7195dfd0153d3c63196932c","tid":1568751,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:18:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"998acad5c3942448f2da305aa107fba4de2d0659","tid":1568751,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:18:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b19f9d27012980e5507a76dd715eb54e664e869a","tid":1568751,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"a1077008f103e0eddddbf665172a991c4516610f","tid":1568751,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"008b158541da3090e8ec593e09b49f2641bbf1b7","tid":1568751,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"839a9e9c5d15879757bd44f9bc1d5143b99a9f87","tid":1568751,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:19:25.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{